race.comment: ALTHOFF (2) talented gelding who came with a well-timed run when saluting as fav over 1350m at Wyong with the 58kg. Produced a solid set of figures on that occasion and he looks to get an even better set-up for this with Grima's claim. Can raise the bar again. MISS SPACEGIRL (13) has gone to a new level this time in with the two gritty wins from three starts. Can get cover from the draw and unleash her sharp turn of foot. Genuine each way prospect. INTERJECTION (5) scored a well-deserved victory at his third run back when covered ground for a comprehensive win over 1400m at this track. Difficult map today and will be ridden for luck. In peak condition and stays in the calculations. MISS HADES (9) thrown in the deep end after the two good wins with a tidy eighth in the G3 Belle of the Turf Stakes at Gosford. Kept fresh and can't be discounted. PUNTIN (3) knocked up late on resumption and undefeated in two second-up runs. Cross-over nose band comes off and capable of better.
